(18, 7, '关于退货退款', '<!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">我们公司主要通过跨境采购为顾客提供采购服务，自身并不加工和制造任何商品。除发运前增加的二次包装外，不对商品自身做任何更改。所有经由我们下单、采购商品的客户，都是根据自身意愿和需要自主下单，并自愿委托</span><span lang="EN-US">我们</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">代办商品的邮寄事宜。</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">因此，如果商品无质量问题，请恕我们无法为已售出的商品提供退货、换货服务。但在会员订购商品有误时，我们会根据实际情况，对部分商品提供换货服务。如果商品质量有问题，我们将尽力协助客户向生产商、快递公司申请调查、理赔。具体情况如下</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">关于已出货、未送达商品的异常申报与理赔：</span></p>\r\n<div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center"><span lang="EN-US">  <hr width="100%" size="2" align="center" />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">1</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、已出货的商品：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">为了确保食品安全、客户的人身安全，保健品、食品、化妆品、美容护肤品等商品一旦发货，如无质量问题，将不可申请退货、换货。如果客户无法接受此条款，请勿下单。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果客户因个人原因就可退换的产品申请退货、换货，我们</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">将在与客户协商确认退货、换货细节后为客户办理退货、换货。相关的到账手续费、退款手续费、扣货费、操作费、折价费等将由客户承担。（请客户在退货、换货前咨询详细的退费标准及具体操作要求）</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">2</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、</span><span lang="ZH-CN"> </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">已到账、未发货的商品：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果自订单确认到账之日起未满</span><span lang="EN-US">10</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">个工作日且客户就未发货商品申请退款、换货，则客户需承担订单的操作费、到账手续费、退款手续费（即银行转账手续费）。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果自订单确认到账之日起已超过</span><span lang="EN-US">10</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">个工作日且客户就未发货商品申请退款、换货，则</span><span lang="EN-US">我们</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">在未发货商品全额退款时不得收任何手续费。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">关于已送达商品的异常申报与理赔：（会员在签收包裹时务必开箱验收）</span></p>\r\n<div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center"><span lang="EN-US">  <hr width="100%" size="2" align="center" />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">1</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、</span><span lang="ZH-CN"> </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">商品破损、错发、少发、货不对板：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">客户在验收包裹时如发现送达的商品与实际订购的商品不附，应当场拒收并在</span><span lang="EN-US">2</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">天内向本公司申报。我们将在收到客户申报之后审核，审核无误后将根据相关的规定为客户安排退换。（我们会承担因退换货产生的相关费用）</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如商品在送达时有异常情况（包括商品破损、错发、少发、货不对版以外的其它异常），但客户未当着快递员的面当场验收包裹，则客户必须于签收后的两天内补齐相关证据。如果客户无法提供完整、有效的相关证据、快递证明，我们将可能无法受理理赔申请。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">关于破损、错发、少发、货不对板的商品，在客户申报异常后，我们有权要求客户提供详尽的照片、视频协助调查。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;2</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、瘪罐商品：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果商品未破损，则客户不得因商品瘪罐而申请退货、换货。（如果无法接受未破损的瘪罐商品，请勿下单。）</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">退款确认与撤销：</span></p>\r\n<div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center"><span lang="EN-US">  <hr width="100%" size="2" align="center" />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">由于部分客户在提出退款申请后想撤销退款申请，为了避免退款申请的确认、撤销出现问题，客户如果确认需要申请退款、撤销退款申请，必须通过以下其中一种方式确认：订单留言、</span><span lang="EN-US">QQ</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">在线客服、邮件。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果客户未通过订单留言、</span><span lang="EN-US">QQ</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">在线客服或邮件确认退款申请、撤销申请，将不为客户办理扣货、退款、撤销退款申请。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">退款时间：</span></p>\r\n<div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center"><span lang="EN-US">  <hr width="100%" size="2" align="center" />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">客户确认处理方案并提供相关的收款账号之后将在</span><span lang="EN-US">10</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">个工作日内安排退款。如因客户提供的相关收款账户信息有误，时间将以客户重新提供收款账号信息后的</span><span lang="EN-US">10</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">个工作日内安排退款。（请客户务必确认相关开户行的账户信息及开户支行是否正确）</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">特殊情况不予理赔的说明：</span></p>\r\n<div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center"><span lang="EN-US">  <hr width="100%" size="2" align="center" />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果遇到以下类似情况，将由消费者自行承担其中风险。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">1. </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">因节假日等原因导致的航班延误、运输延误等情况。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">例如：春节导致的各地包裹数量剧增，包裹派送时效延长；</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">2. </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">因不可抗逆因素（例如：发货限制、清关限制、特殊事件、气候影响）出现的延误或异常的情况。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">例如：奥运会等重大事件导致包裹等待查验的时间加长。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">3. </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果产品无质量问题且未过期，客户不得因为产品的生产日期不够新鲜而申请退货、换货。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">4. </span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">如果产品无质量问题且未过期，客户不得因为购物小票、报纸未随货发送而申请退货、换货。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">注意：为了确保食品安全、客户的人身安全，保健品、食品、化妆品、美容护肤品等商品一旦发货，如无质量问题，将不可申请退货、换货。</span></p>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>