-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="EN-US">1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">小熊卡种类和功能</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">北美商城小熊储值卡（以下称&ldquo;小熊卡&rdquo;）指由加拿大极地熊集团（&ldquo;本公司&rdquo;）发行的，可以在</span><span lang="EN-US">www.pbccstore.com </span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">（&ldquo;本网站&rdquo;）上兑付商品或服务的预付卡。小熊卡仅限在本网站购买产品和服务使用。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">小熊卡分为加币与人民币两种。加币小熊卡充值的面值有</span><span lang="EN-US">20</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，</span><span lang="EN-US">50</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，</span><span lang="EN-US">100</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">；人民币小熊卡充值的面值有</span><span lang="EN-US">100</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，</span><span lang="EN-US">500</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，</span><span lang="EN-US">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="EN-US">2.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">限制</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">2.1<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">充值：会员可在本网站的&ldquo;用户中心&rdquo;内点击&ldquo;充值&rdquo;进行小熊卡充值。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">2.2<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">使用：小熊卡使用前，会员需将金额充入本网站账户&ldquo;小熊卡余额&rdquo;中，如不进行充值将无法使用。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="EN-US">3.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">权利和义务</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">3.1<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">权利和限制</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:-3.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">）</span> <span style="font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibr