(1641, 138, 'NB0194', '西班牙好诺阿拉贡巧克力千层酥饼 105g', '+', 281, 556, '', 98, '0.150', '0.00', '20.80', '0.00', 0, 0, 1, '进口 零食 酥脆千层', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="750" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-spacing: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n    <tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n        <tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n            <td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n            <p style="margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: ''microsoft yahei''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;">规格：105克</span></p>\r\n            <p style="margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';">产地：西班牙</span></p>\r\n            <p style="margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';">配料：小麦粉，植物人造油，水，乳化剂，食用盐，酸度调节剂，防腐剂，食用香料，抗氧化剂，着色剂，可可和榛子奶油夹心，脱脂奶粉，脱脂可可粉，榛子酱，乳清粉，乳化剂，白砂糖，蜂蜜，防腐剂。</span></p>\r\n            <div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';">产品特点:</span></div>\r\n            <div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';">好诺&middot;阿拉贡酥饼，精心选料，传统工艺，不带丝毫的粗糙和生硬，酥脆中享用天然的原料。</span></div>\r\n            <div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''microsoft yahei'';">薄薄的夹饼与果酱在口中融合，甜度恰到好处。